{
  "stem": "12337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She's deaf, and mute, and paralyzed, and-- but my mind was working.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew what was going on, but I couldn't communicate for a long time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at that time is when we met one of my father's clients that he used to deal with.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, he was a farmer that lived three kilometers from-- from our town in Szubkow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He must have heard what had happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came, and he looked at my mother and I, and he was like crying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He couldn't believe that was-- this happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have-- I heard him say, well, what did this child do to deserve this?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he started coming around, bringing eggs and butter once in a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is how our friendship started with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what was his name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Pavlo Garasimchuk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It existed for over a year, all through the time the Germans were in and out of our town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They set up-- it was called a Kehillah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you ever hear that, Kehillah?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like a Jewish government.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They appointed a few people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they drove in with the trucks, the Germans, they would demand certain things they wanted from the people in the town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would want, like, say, diamonds, or furs, or jewelry, gold, all kinds of stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these people knew everyone in town, and they would go around collecting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said if they don't get their things within a certain amount of time, they're going to take 40, 50 people and kill.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every-- so, you know, this was the Kehillah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a very frightening time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would come in every few weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
